Author: button_eyed_coraline
Text: I am Trying To Recover^TM so I mix up 3 servings (1200 cal) with 2 servings of Isopure protein (flavorless) for a grand total of 1400 calories and 110g of protein. Losertown assures me that I will still lose slowly. But that’s more nutrition than I’ve had in a long time and I feel way more awake and alert.   Watch out for the poops tho, Soylent messes with my digestive tract.

Author: BluntCakes_
Text: I have the bottles at 400cal. It’s scary at first a bit, but sometimes I’ll use it as an OMAD that I sip on throughout the day. Definitely makes me feel clearer and have more energy than the same amount of calories in anything else.
